[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.8.2"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 1.8.2 are now fixed in Tails 2.0.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails 2.0|news/version_2.0]] as soon as possible.

Details
=======

* Tor Browser: [[!mfsa2016 01]], [[!mfsa2016 03]]
* sudo: [[!debsa2016 3440]]
* perl: [[!debsa2016 3441]]
* isc-dhcp: [[!debsa2016 3442]]
* libpng: [[!debsa2016 3443]]
* openssh: [[!debsa2016 3446]]
* linux: [[!debsa2016 3448]]
* bind9: [[!debsa2016 3449]]
* fuse: [[!debsa2016 3451]]
